    • getWorlds

      public Collection<MultiverseWorld> getWorlds()

      Get a list of all worlds that may or may not be loaded. It will an LoadedMultiverseWorld if the world is loaded, otherwise you will get an MultiverseWorld instance.

      If you want only unloaded worlds, use getUnloadedWorlds(). If you want only loaded worlds, use getLoadedWorlds().

      Returns:
      A list of all worlds that may or may not be loaded.
